 implemented not only improved the\nisolation performance but also greatly simplified the assembly, testing, and\ncommissioning process. During the past two years, five units have been\nconstructed, tested, installed and commissioned at each of the two LIGO\nobservatories. Five other units are being built for an upcoming third\nobservatory. The test results presented show that the system meets the motion\nrequirements, and reach the sensor noise in the control bandwidth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jul 2014 18:25:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-24"}
