avily changing\nthe functionalities of the model.\n  In general, FASTCORMICS outperforms competing algorithms and allows obtaining\nhigh-quality, robust models in a high-throughput manner. This will allow the\nuse of metabolic modelling as routine process for the analysis of microarray\ndata e.g. in the field of personalized medicine.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Jul 2014 11:34:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-25"}
